hat feels even more conspicuously like an Agatha Christie homage before an extremely clever series of twists kick in. Writer-director Rian Johnson again assembles a solid cast behind Daniel Craig, but it\'s his use of language -- where nary a word is wasted -- that finally gives the sequel its edge.','https://www.cnn.com/2022/11/23/entertainment/glass-onion-a-knives-out-mystery-review/index.html','Wed, 23 Nov 2022 14:00:36 GMT'),(12,5,2066,'\'Love Actually\' cast to reunite for 20th anniversary TV special','One of the most beloved modern Christmas classics is turning 20 next year, and to mark the occasion, cast members from the landmark 2003 romantic comedy \"Love Actually\" are reuniting for a TV special to air on ABC next week, the network announced Tuesday.','https://www.cnn.com/2022/11/22/entertainment/love-actually-20th-anniversary-abc-special/index.html','Wed, 23 Nov 2022 23:02:35 GMT'),(12,5,2067,'James Cameron almost didn\'t choose Leonardo DiCaprio or Kate Winslet to star in \'Titanic\'','James Cameron is sharing some surprising details from the making of his blockbuster hit \"Titanic,\" which celebrates 25 years of being released next month.','https://www.cnn.com/2022/11/22/entertainment/james-cameron-leonardo-dicaprio-kate-winslet-titanic/index.html','Wed, 23 Nov 2022 15:24:00 GMT'),(12,6,2068,'UFC president Dana White does not expect punishment for domestic violence incident','Ultimate Fighting Championship (UFC) president Dana White said he does not expect punishment after a video emerged of him in a physical altercation with his wife earlier this month. White made the comments Wednesday at a media day for UFC Fight Night 217.','https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/12/sport/dana-white-ufc-domestic-violence-spt-intl/index.html','Thu, 12 Jan 2023 18:01:53 GMT'),(12,6,2069,'Lionel Messi scores for Paris Saint-Germain in first game back since World Cup triumph ','Lionel Messi celebrated his return to Paris Saint-Germain with a goal in his first game back since lifting the World Cup.','https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/12/football/lionel-messi-psg-world-cup-return-spt-intl/index.html','Thu, 12 Jan 2023 08:51:54 GMT'),(12,6,2070,'Zach Johnson isn\'t discounting Tiger Woods for the Ryder Cup','Tiger Woods could form part of the US Ryder Cup team -- or at least, Zach Johnson isn\'t ruling it out. ','https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/12/golf/tiger-woods-zach-johnson-ryder-cup-intl-spt/index.html','Thu, 12 Jan 2023 16:53:03 GMT'),(12,6,2071,'Australian Open draw: Rafael Nadal begins title defense with tough test in opening round','Defending champion Rafael Nadal will face English youngster Jack Draper in the opening round of the Australian Open in a bid to retain his 2022 crown and extend his grand slam tally.','https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/12/tennis/australian-open-draw-nadal-djokovic-swiatek-spt-intl/index.html','Thu, 12 Jan 2023 11:22:31 GMT'),(12,6,2072,'The Boston Celtics become the first team to hit 30 wins this season with victory over the New Orleans Pelicans','The Boston Celtics became the first team in the NBA this season to reach 30 wins after beating the New Orleans Pelicans 125-114 at TD Garden in Boston on Wednesday night, largely behind a combined 72 points from the team\'s stars, Jayson Tatum and Jaylen Brown. ','https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/12/sport/boston-celtics-30-wins-pelicans-nba-spt-intl/index.html','Thu, 12 Jan 2023 10:47:18 GMT'),(12,6,2073,'Australia pulls out of Afghanistan cricket series over Taliban\'s restrictions on women','Australia\'s men\'s cricket team has withdrawn from a series of upcoming matches against Afghanistan in protest over the ruling Taliban\'s restrictions on women and girls\' education and employment, Cricket Australia (CA) said in a statement Thursday.','https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/12/sport/australia-afghanistan-cricket-taliban-intl-hnk-spt/index.html','Thu, 12 Jan 2023 16:28:12 GMT'),(12,6,2074,'Damar Hamlin has been released after spending more than a week hospitalized due to a cardiac arrest ','Damar Hamlin has been released after being hospitalized for more than a week due to a cardiac arrest he suffered during a \"Monday Night Football\" game earlier this month, the Buffalo Bills tweeted Wednesday.','https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/11/sport/damar-hamlin-buffalo-bills-hospital-release-spt/index.html','Wed, 11 Jan 2023 18:37:03 GMT'),(12,6,2075,'Pelé\'s final hurrah at New York Cosmos helped spark \'sporting revolution\' ','He\'d won three World Cups, scored goals galore and become a global icon, but Pelé wasn\'t quite done yet, so off he went to the US and helped transform the sport of soccer in North America. ','https://www.cnn.com/2022/12/31/football/pele-new-york-cosmos-north-america-revolution-spt-intl/index.html','Sat, 31 Dec 2022 10:55:43 GMT'),(12,6,2076,'What made Pelé so great','Born into poverty -- he used to kick a grapefruit around Brazil\'s Minas Gerais state -- Pelé finished his career as arguably soccer\'s greatest ever player.','https://www.cnn.com/2022/12/30/football/what-made-pele-great-spt-intl/index.html','Fri, 30 Dec 2022 10:33:38 GMT'),(12,6,2077,'Pelé\'s life in pictures','By Kyle Almond and Will Lanzoni, CNN','https://www.cnn.com/2022/12/29/football/gallery/pele-life-in-pictures/index.html','Sun, 16 Apr 2023 20:39:48 GMT'),(12,6,2078,'Iranian chess referee fears ostracism over her activism','Three years after fleeing Iran, chess referee Shohreh Bayat fears being further ostracized after challenging the game\'s governing body and its president, Russia\'s former deputy prime minister, over her choice of clothing at a tournament in October.','https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/12/sport/iranian-chess-referee-shohreh-bayat-russia-spt-intl/index.html','Thu, 12 Jan 2023 09:35:28 GMT'),(12,6,2079,'NFL coach controversy: \'It\'s not about race. It\'s about finding quality coaches\'','When Lovie Smith was hired by the Houston Texans in February 2022 as the team\'s new head coach, he said the NFL had \"a problem\" with hiring Black coaches and diversity.','https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/10/sport/nfl-lovie-smith-diversity/index.html','Wed, 11 Jan 2023 11:46:19 GMT'),(12,6,2080,'Racing yacht just keeps on giving in extraordinary ways','More than three decades since its pioneering, round-the-world voyage, the Maiden racing yacht is again sailing the high seas -- and changing the lives of young women in the process. ','https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/10/sport/maiden-sailing-tracy-edwards-spt-intl/index.html','Tue, 10 Jan 2023 14:29:08 GMT'),(12,6,2081,'From feminist pioneers to putting pros, the historic journey of the world\'s oldest ladies golf club','Who would you back to sink a putt to save your life? Tiger Woods? Jack Nicklaus? Ben Crenshaw? ','https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/10/golf/st-andrews-ladies-putting-club-spt-spc-intl/index.html','Tue, 10 Jan 2023 10:17:29 GMT'),(12,6,2082,'Jon Rahm produces stunning comeback to win Tournament of Champions in Hawaii','Spanish golfer Jon Rahm won his third PGA Tour title in six starts with a stunning comeback to overturn a seven-shot deficit at the Tournament of Champions in Hawaii.','https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/09/golf/jon-rahm-comeback-pga-tours-tournament-of-champions-hawaii-spt-intl/index.html','Mon, 09 Jan 2023 12:23:12 GMT'),(12,6,2083,'Georgia realtor receives invitation to play the Masters by mistake ','Scott Stallings arrived at his condo on Georgia\'s Saint Simons Island to find a package holding the most prestigious letter in golf.','https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/02/us/scott-stallings-masters-invitation-mix-up/index.html','Tue, 03 Jan 2023 09:14:05 GMT'),(12,6,2084,'Why Cristiano Ronaldo\'s move to Saudi Arabia means so much for the Gulf monarchy\'s sporting ambitions  ','It\'s a partnership that\'s been hailed as \"history in the making.\"  ','https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/06/football/ronaldo-saudi-soccer-sport-mime-intl/index.html','Fri, 06 Jan 2023 12:32:00 GMT'),(12,7,2085,'Mars Science Lab launch delayed two years','NASA\'s launch of the Mars Science Laboratory -- hampered by technical difficulties and cost overruns -- has been delayed until the fall of 2011, NASA officials said at a news conference Thursday in Washington.','http://edition.cnn.com/2008/TECH/space/12/04/nasa.mars.delay/index.html?eref=edition_space','Fri, 05 Dec 2008 10:34:54 EST'),(12,7,2086,'Shuttle lands at California air base','NASA officials Sunday waved off the first opportunity for space shuttle Endeavour to return to Earth, citing poor weather conditions.','http://edition.cnn.com/2008/TECH/space/11/30/space.shuttle/index.html?eref=edition_space','Mon, 01 Dec 2008 00:17:51 EST'),(12,7,2087,'iReporters watch planets, moon align','','http://edition.cnn.com/2008/TECH/space/12/02/planetsalign.irpt/index.html?eref=edition_space','Tue, 02 Dec 2008 12:52:24 EST'),(12,7,2088,'Inspiration for \'Contact\' still listening','From a remote valley in Northern California, Jill Tarter is listening to the universe.','http://edition.cnn.com/2008/TECH/space/11/26/aliens.tarter/index.html?eref=edition_space','Wed, 26 Nov 2008 12:02:33 EST'),(12,7,2089,'Indian lunar orbiter hit by heat rise','Scientists have switched off several on-board instruments to halt rising temperatures inside India\'s first unmanned lunar spacecraft.','http://edition.cnn.com/2008/TECH/space/11/26/india.moon.probe/index.html?eref=edition_space','Wed, 26 Nov 2008 07:26:44 EST');
